8.	min li-mu-um erin₂-bi nu-ŋál
9.	x x-ne nu-un-DU nu-un-gi₄
10.	ha-ra-kalag lugal-ŋu₁₀ mu-un-taka₄ mu-un-dab₅
11.	NIR-da-bi NIR-da lugal-ŋu₁₀ [ba-e]-dugud
12.	[...]-ma lugal? [...]x
13.	[...]x ni x[...]-ŋar
