3.	arad-zu na-ab-bé-a
4.	ka-ku-la-tum{ki}-šè gaba-ri gíd-da-ŋu₁₀-ne
5.	mar-tu {ŋiš}tukul-bi-da šubtu₅-ta im-ma-zig
6.	ŋe₂₆-e zi-ga-ŋu₁₀-ne 600 [ì]-gaz 1200 ì-dab₅
7.	ka-ku-la-tum{ki}-šè ba-ni-kur₉
8.	tukum-bi lugal-ŋu₁₀ ugnim-ma tuš-ù-bi ab-bé
9.	kuša-ŋá-lá keše₂-da-bi šu hé-mi-ib-da₁₃-da₁₃
10.	tukum-bi lugal-ŋu₁₀ ugnim-ma nu-tuš-ù-bi ab-bé
